	<entry>
		<title>José Carlos Dias</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://cnv.memoriasreveladas.gov.br/institucional-acesso-informacao/membros/43-textos_do_conselho/631-textos-de-jose-carlos-dias-2.html"/>
		<published>2014-04-09T15:55:14-03:00</published>
		<updated>2014-04-09T15:55:14-03:00</updated>
		<id>http://cnv.memoriasreveladas.gov.br/institucional-acesso-informacao/membros/43-textos_do_conselho/631-textos-de-jose-carlos-dias-2.html</id>
		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;feed-description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12/03/2014 - &lt;/strong&gt;Exposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de Jos&amp;eacute; Carlos Dias na mesa Justi&amp;ccedil;a de transi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e a Comiss&amp;atilde;o da Verdade, no &lt;strong&gt;Semin&amp;aacute;rio 1964: 50 anos depois&lt;/strong&gt;, organizado pelo Cebrap em S&amp;atilde;o Paulo. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YvtjrmFGAnk&amp;amp;list=PLxI8Can9yAHcxLg1t0wu8OdGrEFWxdFNX&amp;amp;index=33&quot;&gt;Em v&amp;iacute;deo&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;30/03/2014 -&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;index.php/component/content/article/2-uncategorised/468-precisamos-extirpar-as-metastases-da-ditadura&quot;&gt;Precisamos extirpar as met&amp;aacute;stases da ditadura&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Texto publicado originalmente no Brasil Post&lt;/p&gt;
